   "itemId": "173",
   "html": "<p class=\"default-note\" _item_id=\"173\"><strong>NOTE:</strong> The sub-agencies presented in this section represent awarding organizations and were sourced from the General Services Administration (GSA) Federal Hierarchy (available at <a>https://sam.gov/content/hierarchy</a>). This award hierarchy establishes the relationship between a department or independent agency’s sub-tiers and its offices and is used by federal agencies as the authoritative source for managing federal funding and awarding organizations.</p>"
